a, Pietro Mascagni, Teatro delle Muse"> </span> </footer></div> </article><div id="author-block" class="box-shadow-2px clearfix" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"><h2 class="author-title">About the author</h2><div id="author-avatar"> <img itemprop="image" style="display:none;" src="http://gravatar.com/avatar/a482ad643dfdd4893232b5c8887b9fbf" alt="" /> <img src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/IMG_3710-150x150.jpg" width="100" height="100" alt="Davide Oliviero" class="avatar avatar-100 wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-100 alignnone photo" /></div><div id="author-description" class="padding-20"><meta itemprop="name" content="Davide Oliviero"><meta itemprop="url" content=""><p></p><p class="add-author-info"> <a href="#"><i class="icon-facebook-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-twitter-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-google-plus-sign"></i></a></p> <a style="font-size: 11px;" href="http://www.gbopera.it/author/davide-oliviero/">View all articles by Davide Oliviero</a></div></div><div class="nav-block box-shadow-2px padding-20 clearfix"> <nav class="nav-single"><h3 class="assistive-text">Post navigation</h3> <span class="nav-previous"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2013/01/verdi-e-il-potere-modelli-letterari-arie-e-balletti-per-un-anniversario/" rel="prev"><span class="meta-nav">&larr;</span> &#8220;Verdi e il potere&#8221;: modelli letterari, arie e balletti per un anniversario</a></span> <span class="nav-next"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2013/01/trieste-teatro-verdiil-corsaro/" rel="next">Trieste, Teatro Verdi:&#8221;Il Corsaro&#8221; <span class="meta-nav">&rarr;</span></a></span> </nav><nav class="nav-single-hidden"> <span class="nav-previous"></span> <span class="nav-next"></span><div class="clear"></div> </nav></div><div class="comments-block box-shadow-2px clearfix"><div id="comments" class="comments-area"><div id="respond" class="comment-respond"><h3 id="reply-title" class="comment-reply-title">Lascia un commento <sm